title: PM meets President-elect Zardari, congratulates on election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Mar 09 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif Saturday met President-elect Asif Ali Zardari at Zardari House here and congratulated him on becoming President for the second time.
The Prime Minister expressed best wishes for President-elect Asif Ali Zardari. President-elect
Zardari thanked the Prime Minister for support of Pakistan Muslim League (N) in the election for President.
